<p>Also, note how he takes pains to throw insignificant metrics around whenever describing a person, but <i>places</i> get nothing at all, or at most an entirely unbelievable "lindo", when you know i.e. that gym is a matchbox on the fifth floor of a rotting hruscheva, reeking of black mold and lit with a solitary, bare LED bulb.</p>
